<h2>The weather in September 2020</h2>
<h3>Temperature deviations and extremes</h3>
Daily minimum temperatures were below the 1981-2010 average especially in Germany (Figure 3). The maximum temperatures were higher than normal in the east Mediterranean countries like Turkey and in countries adjacent to the Black sea.
