<h3>Radiation and Cloudiness</h3>
The global radiation anomaly based on E-OBS (Figure 14) shows a positive anomaly in Italy and a negative anomaly in the Cote d'Azur (France). These details are not captured by the remote sensing data. The incoming surface radiation based on Seviri/Mviri data (Figure 15) is above the average in central Europe. The monthly cloud cover anomaly based on AVHRR data (Figure 16) shows a corresponding underestimated cloud cover in the same area.
